query:
UPDATE aggregator.user_history_limit
                        SET prev = (
                            SELECT prev
                            FROM aggregator.user_history_limit
                            WHERE market_id = $1
                            AND order_id = $2
                        )
                        WHERE market_id = $1
                        AND price = (
                            SELECT price
                            FROM aggregator.user_history_limit
                            WHERE market_id = $1
                            AND order_id = $2
                        )
                        AND prev = $2;
